                            <comment id="14480503" author="paulk" created="Thu, 8 May 2014 05:30:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Might be a job for &quot;git bisect&quot; but do you happen to know the last known Groovy version where this worked? 2.2.2? 2.2.3-SNAPSHOT? One of the 2.3 betas? Ta.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14475937" author="russel" created="Thu, 8 May 2014 07:13:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Easier to use GVM and have lots of Groovy versions installed. 2.2.2 works fine, 2.3.0 fails, 2.3.1-SNAPSHOT fails.  Of course this doesn&apos;t help with the exact version of 2.3.0-SNAPSHOT. I&apos;ll see if I can do the bisect now that I have a known working version.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14475940" author="melix" created="Mon, 12 May 2014 10:15:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;So bisect says:&lt;/p&gt;

